e to stop by the CCC to discuss your plans and see what scholarships you may qualify for, passes can be given by\u00a0Danea Cramer in A-26 for advocacy.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Follow the CCC @nw_ccc on Twitter for all of the latest information related to life after high school.\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>It&#8217;s time to make scholarships your focus! You can find opportunities through nonprofit organizations, and small and large companies. Ask your employer, your parent\u2019s employer, and your church. You never know where an opportunity may exist. What should you do? Schedule time in your week to work on scholarship applications. It can quickly feel overwhelming,&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0,"footnotes":""},"categories":[459,4],"tags":[103,93],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2526"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2526"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2526\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2534,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2526\/revisions\/2534"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2526"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2526"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nort